u": "Yes, it was guarded, but still . . ."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1669.641","u": "Who guarded the border, the Poles or . . ."},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1671.671","u": "The Poles and Russians."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1672.755","u": "Poles and Russians. So you got across?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1675.376","u": "Yes."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1675.852","u": "Where did you eat? What did you get to eat?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1678.111","u": "I took something along from Poland yet, and in Berlin I already received [help] from the Jewish committee."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1683.533","u": "You went in, directly to the American zone?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1687.672","u": "Yes."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1688.377","u": "And there was a Jewish committee?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1689.684","u": "Yes."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1690.166","u": "Who were they, Americans or Germans?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1691.672","u": "No. Jewish . . . Jews, Jewish Americans."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1694.534","u": "Hm. And they took you from there to where?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1698.793","u": "They sent me over to Hannover in the English zone."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1701.504","u": "The English zone. All right, and from there?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1703.624","u": "And from there again to the American zone, Frankfurt, Munich."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1707.299","u": "Yes, and then?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1709.438","u": "And then I went on already by myself. By train to Saarbruecken [sp?] and from Saarbruecken . . . "},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1714.902","u": "With what did you buy a ticket?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1716.782","u": "I still had some money on me."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1719.113","u": "From where?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1719.866","u": "From Poland. I had been working."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1722.005","u": "When did you work in Poland. After you returned?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1723.915","u": "After the liberation. The few months after liberation."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1725.644","u": "What did you work at?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1727.042","u": "I made maps [sketched?]."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1728.922","u": "Are you a draftsman?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1730.109","u": "Yes."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1731.416","u": "What were you paid for it?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1733.193","u": "I made a few hundred Zlotys a day."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1736.868","u": "And what . . . what did the food cost? Or did [you get] the food . . ."},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1740.513","u": "It was about enough to live on without too much luxury."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1744.471","u": "Yes. [Chuckle.] And then you bought your ticket . . ."},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1748.790","u": "Yes."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1749.152","u": ". . . and you came to Paris."},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1750.128","u": "To Saarbruecken and from there again across the border again on foot."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1754.146","u": "Yes? Did you smuggle yourself across the border?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1758.634","u": "Yes."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1759.236","u": "Why?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1759.959","u": "I was not able to get a visa."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1762.761","u": "But your uncle [brother] was here."},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1765.725","u": "It was impossible. I had to take too much time. I was in the French consulate in Baden-Baden. He told me it had to take half a year, maybe longer."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1774.623","u": "The French consul."},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1775.418","u": "Yes."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1776.834","u": "Nu?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1777.900","u": "[Words not clear.]"},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1779.617","u": "So you crossed the border."},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1781.015","u": "Yes."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1781.780","u": "And then . . . could you live here in Paris if you crossed the border?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1787.654","u": "Yes."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1788.268","u": "Yes, and with whom are you staying here in Paris?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1790.829","u": "I am staying with my brother."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1792.739","u": "Oh, you are staying with your brother."},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1793.986","u": "Yes."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1794.691","u": "And in what business is your brother?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1796.480","u": "He is a doctor of medicine."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1798.438","u": "Oh, he is a physician."},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1799.986","u": "Physician."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1801.703","u": "What . . . has he always lived here in France?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1803.571","u": "Yes, he studied here. He finished his studies here and was here already."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1807.951","u": "Hm, and what do you now?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1810.343","u": "Now I am learning TSF [radio] and go on with painting."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1814.482","u": "And what are your plans for the future?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1817.476","u": "Hm . . . to go working at TSF."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1820.139","u": "What?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1820.753","u": "TSF. Radio."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1822.139","u": "And . . ."},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1822.410","u": "They call it in French: telegraphie sans fil."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1826.296","u": "Hm. TSF. You want . . . what do you want to do in radio?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1830.916","u": "To become a radio mechanic. Set assembling."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1833.808","u": "Set assembling and so forth."},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1834.983","u": "Installations."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1835.808","u": "Do you want to open up a store later on, or what?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1838.399","u": "Perhaps. At first I must learn the job, and then when I stand on my own feet and when it is possible, then I would like very much . . . [pause]"},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1851.152","u": "What?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1852.688","u": ". . . to work for myself."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1853.803","u": "Hm. Do you want to remain in France?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1855.773","u": "Yes."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1860.303","u": "Hm. Yes. Well, this is more or less a clear story. There are some particulars which . . . which we did not know too well. I wonder if you would do me a small favor. [Here follows one of the few attempts to administer a modified Thematic Apperception Test which was soon given up as greatly time consuming and falling outside the scope of the project.] Tell me, what does this picture remind you of? What would you think of this picture? What memories does it evoke in you? [Pause.] Were you to compose a story from this picture, what would you say it was?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1915.147","u": "A child . . ."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1916.503","u": "Yes?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1917.178","u": ". . . perhaps an artist, playing the violin . . ."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1921.407","u": "Yes?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1923.859","u": "Looks quite young."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1927.275","u": "And what is this picture?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1934.516","u": "A woman. Looks suffering."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1939.016","u": "Judging by your experience of the last five years, what would you say has happened to this woman?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1950.341","u": "Went through a lot. Has suffered much. That is seen in her face."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1958.624","u": "And what kind of a story does this picture represent?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1968.621","u": "A corpse, a mussulman."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1971.374","u": "What?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1971.856","u": "A mussulman, a sick one."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1975.814","u": "A sick one?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1976.609","u": "Yes."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1976.700","u": "What is a mussulman?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1977.857","u": "A mussulman is a man who is already so weak that he cannot walk by himself."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1983.863","u": "Where does this word come from?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1985.008","u": "Ther Germans originated that word yet."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1987.671","u": "What is the word?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1989.008","u": "Mussulman."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1989.912","u": "How do you spell is? M-U-S . . ."},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1992.123","u": ". . . S-U-L-M-A-N."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1995.207","u": "And that means what?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "1996.804","u": "That means weak people who cannot walk anymore. Sick people."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "2000.461","u": "Hm, and what is this?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "2010.865","u": "Freedom."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "2015.305","u": "Hm, and what is this?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "2021.100","u": "Work."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "2022.968","u": "Tell me more."},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "2025.058","u": "This is our future."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "2027.890","u": "Hm. Now, what do you think of the future? Do you think we shall have war again?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "2040.432","u": "I shall not go to a lager again."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "2042.480","u": "What?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "2044.017","u": "I shall not go to a lager again."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "2045.625","u": "What would you do?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "2047.131","u": "Anything, but not that."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "2049.481","u": "Yes, but it does not . . . it did not depend on you whether to go to a lager."},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "2053.951","u": "Now it shall already depend on me."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "2055.831","u": "What will you do then?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "2057.771","u": "Anything, but not to go to a lager again."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "2060.434","u": "For instance."},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "2062.946","u": "Become a soldier."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "2065.235","u": "Hm."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "2068.910","u": "All right."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "2069.826","u": "Was it then possible for you to become a soldier? How old were you when it started?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "2079.657","u": "Fifteen."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "2081.766","u": "Fifteen, and you are now?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "2083.706","u": "Twenty-one."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "2086.670","u": "[In English] This concludes a record by . . . taken from a young man, Adam Krakowski. He lives now in Paris."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "2101.652","u": "[In German] Is your brother&#39;s name also Krakowski?"},    {"who": "Adam Krakowski", "start": "2103.381","u": "Yes."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "2104.508","u": "[In English] His brother, a long-time practicing physician here in this city . . . He is studying radio at the ORT and plans later to become a radio technician . . . radio man. He does not plan to leave the country. He neither thinks of going to the United States nor Palestine, nor any other place. He is apparently hoping to get set up here."}        ]
    }
_jsready = true;
var return_val;
switch (String(type)){
        case "transcription":
        return_val = transcription.interview;
        break;
            case "english_translation":
        return_val = english_translation.interview;
        break;
    }
return return_val;
}
